--USE CTE
WITH popvsvac 
AS
(
SELECT dea.continent, dea.location, dea.date, population, vac.new_vaccinations
, SUM(CAST(vac.new_vaccinations AS INT64)) OVER (PARTITION BY dea.location ORDER BY dea.location
, dea.date) AS rolling_people_vaccinated
FROM `hallowed-glider-358623.PortfolioProject.covid_deaths` AS dea
JOIN `hallowed-glider-358623.PortfolioProject.covid_vaccinations` AS vac
ON dea.location = vac.location
AND dea.date = vac.date
WHERE dea.continent IS NOT NULL
)
SELECT *, (rolling_people_vaccinated/population)*100 AS percentage_people_vaccinated
FROM popvsvac
